This page is a permanent visual and semantic fixture. It should remain a draft.

## Typography and links

This is a short paragraph. The next paragraph is deliberately longer so line length, wrapping, rhythm, and contrast can be judged across viewport sizes. Technical writing often combines ordinary prose with identifiers such as `AbortController`, flags such as `--inspect`, and links like [the Svelte documentation](https://svelte.dev/docs).

An intentionally long URL should wrap without widening the page: https://example.com/a/very/long/path/that/should/not/cause/the/article/container/to/overflow/on/a/narrow/mobile/viewport?with=a-long-query-value

